          "title": "HealthOmics Ready2Run Workflows",
          "helpText": "Ready2Run workflows are pre-built workflows that have been packaged by industry third party software companies and open-source pipelines. You can simply use Ready2Run workflows to process your data with the most commonly used workflows like Germline and GATK-BP. Ready2Run workflows are pay-per-run which means you are charged the same price for every workflow.",
